k platform activity including:",[238,239,240,248,254],"ul",{},[241,242,243,247],"li",{},[244,245,246],"strong",{},"Login history"," — Who connected, when, and from where",[241,249,250,253],{},[244,251,252],{},"Configuration changes"," — OIDC provider updates, LLM configuration changes, and application settings modifications",[241,255,256,259],{},[244,257,258],{},"Activity counts"," — Aggregate usage metrics per user, application, and organization",[202,261,263],{"id":262},"application-logs","Application Logs",[206,265,266],{},"View microservice logs directly from the dashboard with the ability to temporarily adjust logging levels for debugging. Increase verbosity on a running service to investigate an issue, then restore normal levels when done — no redeployment required.",{"title":268,"searchDepth":269,"depth":269,"links":270},"",2,[271,272,273,274,275,276],{"id":204,"depth":269,"text":25},{"id":211,"depth":269,"text":212},{"id":218,"depth":269,"text":219},{"id":225,"depth":269,"text":226},{"id":232,"depth":269,"text":233},{"id":262,"depth":269,"text":263},"Monitoring, tracing, and logging across your Kinotic applications.","md",null,{},{"icon":160},{"title":157,"description":277},"M6jhdcwtbQS4mGWO4DLBcfRtXE8lPiprnQlyybhWigs",[285,287],{"title":152,"path":153,"stem":154,"description":286,"icon":155,"children":-1},"Platform-level security architecture in Kinotic OS.",{"title":162,"path":163,"stem":164,"description":288,"icon":165,"children":-1},"How to contribute to the Kinotic OS project.",1775161662253]